        <span class="na">platform</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">state'</span>
        <span class="na">to_state</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">on'</span>
      <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">entity_id</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">binary_sensor.b_no_motion_for_20'</span>
        <span class="na">prob_given_true</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="m">1</span>
        <span class="na">prob_given_false</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="m">0.825</span>
        <span class="na">platform</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">state'</span>
        <span class="na">to_state</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">on'</span>
      <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">entity_id</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">binary_sensor.t_no_motion_for_20'</span>
        <span class="na">prob_given_true</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="m">1</span>
        <span class="na">prob_given_false</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="m">0.825</span>
        <span class="na">platform</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">state'</span>
        <span class="na">to_state</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">on'</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>其中，可能醒着的时间段和每个地方是否无人超过20分钟是通过模版实现的：</p>
<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="na">binary_sensor</span><span class="pi">:</span>
  <span class="c1"># 可能醒着的时间段（睡眠时间段的反）</span>
  <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">platform</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">template</span>
    <span class="na">sensors</span><span class="pi">:</span>
      <span class="na">prone_to_wake</span><span class="pi">:</span>
        <span class="na">value_template</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">{{</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">states.sensor.time.state</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">&gt;</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">"09:00"</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">and</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">states.sensor.time.state</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">&lt;=</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">"21:59"}}'</span>
  <span class="c1"># 20分钟无人二进制传感例子</span>
  <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">platform</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">template</span>
    <span class="na">sensors</span><span class="pi">:</span>
      <span class="na">k_no_motion_for_20</span><span class="pi">:</span>
        <span class="na">value_template</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">{{states.binary_sensor.motion_sensor_kitchen.attributes["No</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">motion</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">since"]</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">|</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">int</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">&gt;=</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">1200}}'</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>为了Debug，可以随时监测贝叶斯传感器的触发概率：</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># 贝叶斯睡觉传感器的概率记录，用于debug</span>
<span class="na">sensor</span><span class="pi">:</span>
  <span class="pi">-</span> <span class="na">platform</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">template</span>
    <span class="na">sensors</span><span class="pi">:</span>
      <span class="na">sleeping_probability</span><span class="pi">:</span>
        <span class="na">friendly_name</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">睡觉概率"</span>
        <span class="na">value_template</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">{{</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">states.binary_sensor.sleeping.attributes.probability</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">|</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">float</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">*</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">100</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">}}"</span>
        <span class="na">unit_of_measurement</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">%"</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
:ET